# Copy this file to .env for local config.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the app bundle at build time —
# NEVER put secret API keys here.
#
# The Anthropic key is NO LONGER a client variable. It lives server-side as a
# Supabase secret, used only by the `ember-chat` Edge Function:
#   supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#   supabase functions deploy ember-chat
#
# Supabase URL + anon key currently live in lib/config.ts (gitignored).
# The anon key is safe to expose; RLS protects the data.
